csAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sym1665702678457.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sym1665702678457.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sym1665702678457.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sym1665702678457\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Driver is responsible for releasing any resources it acquired.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sym1665702678457__section_w2074ab1b5b1_w2075ab1b5_w2076ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1233978e49\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Client/server and SMTP security drivers</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sym1665702678457__section_vrt_srp_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1233978e58\">Expected Input</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sym1665702678457__p_d132044e1_d132045e1_d132046e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Properties</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">Parameters</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sym1665702678457__p_d132047e1_d132048e1_d132049e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">InBuf</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">InDataLen</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">InBufLen</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sym1665702678457__p_d132050e1_d132051e1_d132052e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">OutBuf</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutDataLen</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutBufLen</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sym1665702678457__p_d132053e1_d132054e1_d132055e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ErrMsg</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">ErrMsgLen</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sym1665702678457__p_d132056e1_d132057e1_d132058e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DrvArea</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sym1665702678457__section_w2077ab1b5b5_w2078ab1b5_w2079ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1233978e113\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USEC_SUCCESS</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sym1665702678457__section_w2080ab1b5b7_w2081ab1b5_w2082ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1233978e123\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sym1665702678457__p_d132068e1_d132069e1_d132070e1\">This function is called after the connection is closed\n        or if errors have occurred.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sym1665702678457__p_d132071e1_d132072e1_d132073e1\">The driver is no longer required and should\n        de-allocate any resources that have been used.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532236\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532236\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "USEC_CLOSE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 12, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Driver is responsible for releasing any resources it acquired. Use Client/server and SMTP security drivers Expected Input Properties , Parameters InBuf , InDataLen , InBufLen OutBuf , OutDataLen , OutBufLen ErrMsg , ErrMsgLen DrvArea Return Values USEC_SUCCESS Description This function is called after the connection is closed or if errors have occurred. The driver is no longer required and should de-allocate any resources that have been used. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}